name: THE WHALE 🐳
description:
Part 3 of a 3 part series exploring some of the archetypes observed in the NFT space

"A whale is someone who owns a lot of cryptocurrency, in this case Tezos, whales will stumble across your profile and buy everything, regardless of price, and will usually sell them for a high profit."




👁️
